<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
<p class="lead-in">Your privacy is important to us. At website.com believe that all individuals should have control and ownership over their personal data.  We feel these <a href="http://www.attentiontrust.org/principles">Principles</a> set out by the Attention Trust provide great guidance in delivering on this committment.</p>
